Forget this one. Been all over and tried other versions as well. Check out http://www.wilderssecurity.com/showthread.php?t=164861 as well, this is not the kind of software I'd trust for backup.

Great, kaspersky reports clean. It reports "unsafe operations", but of course a sector level disk utility will do that.
Successfully restored two .tib images with this.
